<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٢٠ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">‌إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6555">‌النَّضْرُ </a>قَالَ: أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">‌سُلَيْمَانَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">‌إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4490">‌عَلْقَمَةَ </a>، <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">‌وَالْأَسْوَدِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">‌عَبْدِ اللهِ </a>فَذَكَرَ نَحْوَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>